{"tid":959331,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"又話五青汁過難飲屎嘅，五青汁試飲","createTime":"2018-12-28T13:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T06:53:53.000Z","uid":137579,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"02ea8ed24954e9209d7cf99b1e7b3d9edb65224f","tid":959331,"uid":137579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T13:24:01.000Z","msg":"前幾日，我就同成班仔一齊出去葵廣行街食嘢（屌真係好慘，冇女真係好慘呀），而葵廣最高嗰層就有兩間果汁店，去過嘅人應該都飲過，不過未必人人試過五青汁<br />\n<br />\n五青汁就係指青蘋果、青椒、青瓜、苦瓜及芹菜溝埋嘅嘢飲，不過大家見到呢啲嘢溝埋嘅綠色嘢飲，我相信大家都唔會想試或者想飲，所以今次就試一試呢個五青汁，希望排咁啲毒氣，令到我喺呢個聖誕變得冇咁毒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而我就上網睇過人地啲試飲片，啲人飲完之後通常都係嘔到七彩，我心裏面都打左個底，我都驚我喺大庭廣眾嘔到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而我就叫左杯細嘅五青汁，飲完之後，其實都唔係想像中咁難飲姐，我唔信飲呢杯嘢會令到人有網上嘅反應囉!!呢杯嘢苦就苦嘅，草青味又大，不過唔係完全飲唔到囉，蘋果汁嘅味都幾出，飲落有回甘添<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總括而言，呢杯嘢真係唔係好飲，不過一定冇香港嗰班youtubers 講到咁撚難飲囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n價錢：16蚊 細杯<br />\n<br />\n希望大家支持下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Br7ri21geQK/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=7hwncw4gq3ou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBr7ri21geQK%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3D7hwncw4gq3ou&d=aRFU5jl%2F6F5Wz4cPtDNnQC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=6856f613\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBr7ri21geQK%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3D7hwncw4gq3ou&h=1e9a3f31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Br7ri21geQK/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=7hwncw4gq3ou</a>"},{"pid":"97bbc4839285ff047ed8f4acc266a047c0c1a825","tid":959331,"uid":137579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02ea8ed24954e9209d7cf99b1e7b3d9edb65224f","tid":959331,"uid":13